description: AMUNDI EURO STOXX 50 UCITS ETF seeks to replicate as closely as possible the performance of the EURO STOXX 50 Index, whether the trend is rising or falling. This ETF enables investors to benefit from an exposure to the 50 leading stocks covering countries in the Eurozone, with a single transaction. For further information, please also refer to the KID and the fund prospectus.
name: Amundi EURO STOXX 50 UCITS ETF DR - USD (C)
